<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
Before entering the for_each_linux_driver loop, ldev is unconditionally assigned by ldev = malloc(sizeof(*ldev)); and that pointer is not set to NULL anywhere before the inner check. Therefore the conditional if (!ldev) inside the loop can never be true, making the allocation statement ldev = malloc(sizeof(*ldev)); unreachable in this function path.
</scenario>
